ality Assurance &amp; Training</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Humam Consulting delivers premium expertise in food safety, quality assurance, facility design, and specialized corporate training across the Middle East.\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Humam Consulting,Food Safety,Quality Assurance,Facility Design,Corporate Training,ISO Certifications,Saudi Arabia Consulting\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Humam Consulting | Expert Quality Assurance\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Premium expertise in food safety, quality assurance, facility design, and specialized training.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://humamconsulting.com\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Humam Consulting\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Humam Consulting\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Expert consultancy and quality assurance for the food industry.\"/><link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/brand/Humam-Logo-Short.svg\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0b3bf435.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/images/brand/Humam-Logo-Short.svg\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/images/brand/Humam-Logo-Short.svg\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/a6dad97d9634a72d.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><nav class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__navbar \"><div class=\"container Navbar-module__O8Na-a__inner\"><a href=\"/ar\"><img alt=\"Logo\" width=\"100\" height=\"70\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbrand%2F&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbrand%2F&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbrand%2F&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></a><ul class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__navLinks\